---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Group Coaching & Workshops"
  description="Group coaching containers and workshops with Suniai — collective healing, shared inquiry, and community support."
>

  <section class="bg-sand-light py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-terracotta mb-4">Services</p>
      <div class="text-4xl mb-5">✨</div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl text-bark mb-6">Group Coaching & Workshops</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-bark/70 leading-relaxed">
        Collective containers where shared presence multiplies the healing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
    <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6 text-bark/70 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-bark">The power of group work</h2>
      <p>
        Placeholder description — describe what makes group work uniquely powerful. How does witnessing and being witnessed by others create something that one-on-one sessions can't?
      </p>
      <p>
        What themes do your workshops typically cover? How are the sessions structured? What can participants expect to leave with?
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-bark pt-4">Typical workshop themes</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        {[
          'Identity and self-expression',
          'Boundaries and nervous system regulation',
          'Body literacy and somatic awareness',
          'Purpose and creative living',
          'Relationships and communication',
          'Seasonal living and cyclical rhythms',
        ].map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-terracotta shrink-0"></span>
            {item}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-bark pt-4">Who is this for?</h3>
      <p>
        Placeholder — describe the ideal participant. Are these open to all, or themed for specific groups (women, creatives, etc.)? What prior experience, if any, is helpful?
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-sand rounded-2xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-terracotta mb-4">Workshop Details</p>
        <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm text-bark/70">
          <div><dt class="font-medium text-bark">Format</dt><dd>Half-day & full-day workshops</dd></div>
          <div><dt class="font-medium text-bark">Group size</dt><dd>6–12 participants</dd></div>
          <div><dt class="font-medium text-bark">Location</dt><dd>In-person (venue TBC)</dd></div>
          <div><dt class="font-medium text-bark">Investment</dt><dd>Placeholder pricing</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="block w-full py-3.5 bg-terracotta text-cream font-medium rounded-full text-center hover:bg-bark transition-colors"
      >
        Register Interest
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="block text-center text-sm text-bark/50 hover:text-terracotta transition-colors">
        ← Back to all services
      </a>
    </aside>
  </section>

</Layout>
